## 3. Streak System

You MUST implement:

### Streak Logic
- A streak counts **consecutive days with ZERO excuses logged**
- Streak resets to 0 when an excuse is logged
- Streak increments at midnight if no excuses that day
- Track:
  - `currentStreak` (days)
  - `longestStreak` (all-time best)
  - `streakStartDate`
  - `lastExcuseDate`

### Streak Display
- Prominent display on home screen
- Visual indicator (flame icon, progress bar, etc.)
- Celebration animation when reaching milestones (3, 7, 14, 30 days)
- Show comparison to longest streak

### Edge Cases
- First day of app use starts at 0
- If user logs excuse at 11:59 PM, streak for that day is broken
- Multiple excuses on same day only count as one "broken" day

